==English==

===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|bʰewdʰ}}
{{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|forbeden}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|forbēodan||to forbid, prohibit, restrain, refuse, repeal, annul}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*furibeudaną}}, from {{m|gem-pro|*furi}} + {{m|gem-pro|*beudaną}}. Equivalent to {{prefix|for|bid|t1=from, away|t2=to offer, proclaim|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{cog|nl|verbieden||to forbid}}, {{cog|de|verbieten||to forbid}}, {{cog|da|forbyde||to forbid}}, {{cog|sv|förbjuda||to forbid}}, {{cog|got|𐍆𐌰𐌿𐍂𐌱𐌹𐌿𐌳𐌰𐌽}}.

